Nokia PC Suite can not add or update maps and voices for the Nokia Maps application. This requires Nokia Map Loader or [[Nokia Ovi Suite]], which both require Microsoft Windows with Microsoft .NET framework installed. However, it is possible to download maps for Nokia Maps without need for Nokia Map Loader or Nokia Ovi Suite by pointing a web browser [http://nokiamaps.site666.info directly to the map files on Nokia's Maps server].
